set default deny

interface backup = "eth2"
interface lan = "eth1"
interface wan = "eth0"

table <branch_lan> { 10.70.0.0/24 }
table <voice_hosts> { 10.70.0.20, 10.70.0.21 }

queue bulk on wan bandwidth 50mbit
queue voice on wan bandwidth 5mbit parent bulk

nat on wan from <branch_lan> to any -> wan

pass in on lan proto udp from <voice_hosts> to any port 5060 queue voice
pass in on lan proto udp from <voice_hosts> to any port 10000 queue voice
pass in on lan proto tcp from <branch_lan> to any port 80 queue bulk route-to 192.0.2.1 (wan) keep state
pass in on lan proto tcp from <branch_lan> to any port 443 queue bulk route-to 192.0.2.1 (wan) keep state
pass in on lan proto tcp from <branch_lan> to any port 22 queue bulk route-to 198.51.100.1 (backup) keep state
block in log (all) on wan from any to any
